<h1 id="payment-request-application---overview">Payment Request Application - Overview</h1>
<p>It is simple application to create, view, delete, read payment requests using Angular as frontend. It is deployed on Non-SAP Server.</p>

<h1 id="what-this-application-does">What this application does?</h1>
<p>It allows a user to create, view, search through requests. There are various components in this app. User can fill the basic details like supplier details, invoice details. User can attach the supported documents as well.
Further, user can also view what status of the request is and that too visually.</p>

